      "use": "Supports stationary top-of-book, order-flow, spread, VWAP-to-mid, and adverse-selection features; squared-error training with direction-aware model selection; purged time-series validation; symmetric signal thresholds; and SHAP sign-stability review. Its latency-free results are not imported as evidence."
