      "title": "Universal Features of Price Formation in Financial Markets",
      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.06917",
      "use": "Supports parameter sharing over normalized supply-demand histories. Round 32 tests a stricter within-asset long/short action symmetry and makes no cross-asset claim."
